          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "8Li radioactive beam was produced in a primary 9Be",
                "target by the neutron transfer reaction 9Be(7Li,8Li).",
                "The 9Be production target had a thickness of 16 mu-m",
                "and was mounted in an ISO chamber just before the first",
                "solenoid.The secondary 8Li beam produced in the forward",
                "direction is collected and focused within an angular",
                "range of 2.0deg < theta < 6.0deg by the first solenoid",
                "of the double-superconducting solenoids of the RIBRAS",
                "facility.The energy of the secondary 8Li beam was",
                "23.9 MeV at the center of the carbon target with an",
                "average intensity of about 5.0E+4 pps."
              ]
            }
          ],
